"{\"uid\": \"rte.ie-sport-hockey-2024-0719-1460743-aussie-hockey-player-amputates-finger-for-olympic-dream\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Australian hockey player Matt Dawson has gone to extraordinary lengths to compete at the Paris Olympics, amputating part of a finger to ensure he will be fit for his third Games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 178, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 24, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Australian hockey player\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_field_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 25, \"end\": 36, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Dawson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.8879104449507e-19, \"text\": \"Matt Dawson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Dawson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Dawson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 30-year-old, a silver medallist at the Tokyo Games, was a doubt for Paris after recently breaking the ring finger on his right hand.\", \"from\": 180, \"to\": 316, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 252, \"end\": 257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999997482275692, \"rank\": 2.5177244297530894e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Doctors gave him a choice of amputating part of his finger or letting it recover.\", \"from\": 318, \"to\": 399, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Only one way would ensure he got to Paris.\", \"from\": 400, \"to\": 442, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 436, \"end\": 441, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999997482275692, \"rank\": 2.5177244297530894e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dawson is now set to line up against Ireland on 29 July when face off in their Pool B fixture.\", \"from\": 444, \"to\": 538, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 444, \"end\": 450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dawson_City\", \"score\": 0.9999761632944864, \"rank\": 2.3336579317336596e-05, \"text\": \"Dawson\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dawson_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dawson_City\"}, {\"begin\": 481, \"end\": 488, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9995980256528244, \"rank\": 0.00026026051102439777, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did not have much time to make the decision,\\\" he told Australian broadcaster Seven Network.\", \"from\": 540, \"to\": 634, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 597, \"end\": 607, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.4859487199560173, \"rank\": 0.5555310556457644, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 620, \"end\": 633, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seven_Network\", \"score\": 0.9999999858671346, \"rank\": 1.3895094851006443e-08, \"text\": \"Seven Network\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seven_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seven_Network\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I made the decision then I called my wife and she said, 'I do not want you to make a rash decision'.\", \"from\": 636, \"to\": 737, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I guess I had all the information I needed to make a decision for not only playing in Paris, but for life after and giving myself the best health.\\\"\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 891, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 830, \"end\": 835, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999997482275692, \"rank\": 2.5177244297530894e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Seven Network showed footage of Dawson wearing a protective black guard over his finger.\", \"from\": 893, \"to\": 985, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 897, \"end\": 910, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seven_Network\", \"score\": 0.9999999858671346, \"rank\": 1.3895094851006443e-08, \"text\": \"Seven Network\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seven_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seven_Network\"}, {\"begin\": 929, \"end\": 935, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dawson_City\", \"score\": 0.9999761632944864, \"rank\": 2.3336579317336596e-05, \"text\": \"Dawson\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dawson_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dawson_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Australian men's coach praised Dawson for his courage and commitment, while admitting he was not sure if he would do the same.\", \"from\": 987, \"to\": 1117, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 987, \"end\": 1001, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\", \"score\": 0.9999999294473152, \"rank\": 7.055275184605875e-08, \"text\": \"The Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\"}, {\"begin\": 1022, \"end\": 1028, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dawson_City\", \"score\": 0.9999761632944864, \"rank\": 2.3336579317336596e-05, \"text\": \"Dawson\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dawson_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dawson_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The best way of recovering from it was to just chop the end of the finger off,\\\" coach Colin Batch said.\", \"from\": 1119, \"to\": 1223, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1206, \"end\": 1217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colin_Batch\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Colin Batch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colin_Batch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colin_Batch\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So that's what he decided to do.\", \"from\": 1225, \"to\": 1258, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not something a coach can decide for a player.\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1310, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Full marks to Matt.\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1332, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Obviously he's really committed to playing in Paris.\", \"from\": 1333, \"to\": 1385, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1379, \"end\": 1384, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999997482275692, \"rank\": 2.5177244297530894e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am not sure I would have done it, but he's done it, so great.\\\"\", \"from\": 1386, \"to\": 1450, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Australia, runners-up up to Belgium at Tokyo, will hope to go one better in Paris where the hockey tournament starts 27 July.\", \"from\": 1452, \"to\": 1577, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1452, \"end\": 1461, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9945096024445821, \"rank\": 0.004034120458124574, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/